import { styled } from '@material-ui/core/styles'
import Select from '@material-ui/core/Select'

const CustomSelect = styled(Select)({
    background: '#FFF',
    border: 0,
    borderRadius: 6,
    boxShadow: '0 3px 5px 2px #5656ef',
    color: '#5656ef',
    padding: 15
})

export default CustomSelect
